node.text: School's out for summer ..... and @gordonramsayrestaurants have got all the family covered !

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Gordon Ramsay on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
I’m teaming up with @quickbooks this month to celebrate small businesses and all that they have done to survive, thrive, and give back to our communities. QuickBooks helps small businesses be more successful, and we can all do our part to support the businesses and restaurants around us as we start to get back to the things we love. 

One business I want to shoutout is @phoenixuppermain in Ellicott City, Maryland. In 2020 my team and I helped bring new life to the Phoenix and the City that had been devastated by two catastrophic floods. The new Phoenix was open for just two weeks when COVID hit, a huge blow for them​. But thanks to their resilience and incredibly hard-working team and heads up approach, they’ve become a true inspiration for me and the community in 2021. I can’t wait to experience their hospitality again soon (and hope you do too !)

Drop a comment below to tell me your favourite small businesses and their stories Gx #ad #BackSmallBiz
